= provide(:description, 'XLPLAN pricing. It is a cloud-based service business management software. Employee calendars, business processes automation, analytics and reporting. Save time while managing your salon easily. Free trial!')
= provide(:keywords, 'xlplan, pricing, price, salon, management software, crm, erp, employee calendar, calendar')

/%head
/  %meta{:content => "xlplan pricing", :name => "description"}/
.text-center
  .display-4
    Pricing and editions
  The first step to success starts with a great sales solution. Find the right fit for you.
  Find out what xlplan can do for you
  Free 14-day trial, no credit card required. Try our software and see for yourself!
.container.mb-5.mt-5
  .pricing.card-deck.flex-column.flex-md-row.mb-3
    .card.card-pricing.text-center.px-3.mb-4
      %span.h6.w-60.mx-auto.px-4.py-1.rounded-bottom.bg-warning.text-black.shadow-sm bronze
      .bg-transparent.card-header.pt-4.border-0
        %h1.h1.font-weight-normal.text-warning.text-center.mb-0{"data-pricing-value" => "25"}
          $
          %span.price 7
          %span.h6.text-muted.ml-2 / month
      .card-body.pt-0
        = link_to 'Try for free', new_user_registration_path(plan: 'bronze'), class: 'btn btn-lg btn-warning'
        %ul.list-unstyled.mb-4
          %li 1 Employee
          %li Free implementation
          %li Free support
    .card.card-pricing.text-center.px-3.mb-4
      %span.h6.w-60.mx-auto.px-4.py-1.rounded-bottom.bg-warning.text-black.shadow-sm silver
